# Local Codex review artifacts, keyed by reviewed commit (ADR-0015 §1).
# Evidence for `just ship`, not history — the review is reported by pasting it
# into the PR, so committing it would duplicate the record and bloat the tree.
.review/

# The vendored embedding model (ADR-0024 §4). A build input: fetched from its
# pinned revision and verified against the recorded manifest by `hatch_build.py`,
# then packaged into the wheel and the sdist. Never committed — 58 MiB of
# incompressible binary would be duplicated permanently in every clone.
src/ai_assistant/models/_vendor/

# Editors / OS
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
.DS_Store
